description: The people of Nashville are going bananas for these amazing Italian Ices!These are frozen treats with all-natural flavoring you'll always be able to enjoy. Whether you're craving the classics, like Cherry, Lemon, and Rainbow, or something more like their Mango, Vanilla Chip, or Peanut Butter, Gorilla Ices has you covered.This truck is ready to take Tennessee on a wild ride with the city's new favorite frozen treat!
name: Gorilla Ices
